15
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,440
Water.

16
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,240
Water.

17
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,480
Mingli.

18
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,080
Mingli.

19
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:05,720
Water.

20
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:15,800
Stepmother,

21
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:18,400
