22
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,520
You venomous woman.

23
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:25,800
You made my life worse than death.

24
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:30,160
I won't let you off even if I become a ghost.

25
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,160
Stepmother,

26
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,220
since you're in such pain,

27
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,240
why don't

28
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,600
I give you a quick end.

29
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,600
You dare to kill your stepmother.

30
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,300
You dared to kill the legitimate mother,

31
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,280
