32
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:47,579
You wouldn't dare.

33
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,420
You wouldn't dare.

34
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:52,480
You'll be punished by heaven.

35
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,360
Help!

36
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,079
Mingli,

37
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,600
