38
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,200
Mingli, save me.

39
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:03,720
She's dead.

40
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,200
Mingli.

41
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:17,360
Of these two pills,

42
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:20,920
one can cure the rot poison in your body,

43
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:24,440
and the other can end your life's suffering.

44
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,720
Choose for yourself.

45
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,680
Mingli.

46
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,480
Mingli.

47
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:51,320
Mingli.

48
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:05,960
Qingshu.

49
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,000
How is she?

50
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,160
My lord,

51
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,780
the poison the lady is afflicted with

52
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:23,560
is the Beidi secret poison, Changxiangwang.

53
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,880
This poison is

54
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:26,800
colorless and odorless.

55
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:29,250
Even mixed into food, it is hard to detect.

56
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:32,080
At first, one suffers weakness and coughs up blood,

57
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,010
then wastes away

58
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,320
to bare bones.

59
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:36,050
Quickly prepare the antidote.

60
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,440
This poison.

61
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,280
Jingyan.

62
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:43,920
