63
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:46,880
Ghost Doctor.

64
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,080
I will give you a prescription for the antidote.

65
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:51,280
Just find the medicine according to it.

66
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:52,280
Go.

67
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,140
Will this work?

68
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,720
Don't you know my medical skills?

69
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,360
