75
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,280
Right now.

76
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,800
I want to be your husband

77
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,400
to guard you and protect you.

78
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,240
I don't want you to

79
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,680
