I brought some iced fruits.

101
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,050
Have a taste.

102
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,000
What's wrong?

103
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,860
I had a dream last night

104
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,240
about my father

105
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,780
and the brothers of the Zhenbei Army.

106
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:07,690
I have entered this life-and-death game.

107
00:11:09,160 --> 00:11:12,090
I returned to the capital from the northern frontier

108
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:15,540
just to find the culprit who framed them.

109
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,680
At first,

110
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:23,000
all clues pointed to King Ling.

111
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:28,000
I was also repeatedly assassinated by the Black Armor Guards.

112
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,200
I suspected for a time

113
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:33,000
that they were the same people hunting you.

114
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:34,640
The Northern Di's

115
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:35,800
royal guards.

116
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,160
I always thought

117
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:43,610
this was Xie Yuheng's plot to kill with a borrowed knife.

118
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,520
Years ago,

119
00:11:54,520 --> 00:11:57,120
someone used this Northern Border defense map

120
00:11:57,760 --> 00:11:59,020
to lure my Zhenbei Army

121
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:00,920
into a death trap.

122
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,680
It not only cost my father's life,

123
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,860
but also caused our three thousand soldiers

124
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,160
to never return.

125
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,160
This person,

126
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,100
if it wasn't King Ling,

127
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:26,380
or the Northern Di people.

128
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,360
Could it be...

129
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,320
Father.

130
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:44,640
You used to always praise the Crown Prince for his bravery,

131
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:46,570
but despised me for being useless.

132
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:51,370
But now, the one sitting firmly on this dragon throne

133
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,080
and ruling the world is me.

134
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:58,800
Dafeng has not been at war for ten years.

135
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,480
This map

136
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:03,800
was drawn when I first ascended the throne

137
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:06,720
by me and the Marquis of Zhenbei.

138
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,560
You were able to repair and perfect it.

139
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:10,600
That is very good.

140
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,560
If this war starts,

141
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,220
we will surely win.

142
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,840
The Marquis of Zhenbei has guarded the northern border for years.

143
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:19,520
The three thousand Zhenbei troops are unstoppable.

144
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:23,050
If there is a war, they will definitely achieve a great victory.

145
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,880
Father, please take your medicine.

146
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:29,800
