151
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,160
your intentions,

152
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,320
I understand.

153
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:43,440
However, the position of Crown Prince is not for you to covet.

154
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,640
You

155
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:47,300
