156
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,360
When the Crown Prince ascends the throne,

157
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,420
you must assist him wholeheartedly.

158
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:54,200
That, as a prince,

159
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:57,760
is your greatest duty to Dafeng.

160
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,520
I will strictly do my duty,

161
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:02,560
assist the Crown Prince,

162
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:04,780
honor you, Father,

163
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,290
and remain loyal to Dafeng.

164
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,280
Father!

165
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:13,460
I will have someone brew the medicine again right away.

166
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,280
I shall take my leave.

167
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:43,640
At that time, the Fourth Prince and Prince Ling secretly forged weapons,

168
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:44,760
counterfeited the Empress's seal,

169
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:46,020
forged travel passes,

170
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:48,920
and secretly sold these weapons to the Beidi army

171
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:49,920
