174
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:02,840
The Marquis of Zhenbei was a confidant of the late Emperor

175
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:04,280
and held massive military power.

176
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:05,640
If he had any ambitions,

177
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,700
