180
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,160
The Fourth Prince.

181
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:12,720
Exactly.

182
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:15,800
The Emperor

183
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:19,520
