186
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:26,520
and shifted all the blame onto Prince Ling,

187
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:29,480
while keeping his own hands clean.

188
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:30,800
Since ancient times,

189
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:33,600
