194
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:50,320
He must have been promised huge benefits,

195
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,580
either supreme power,

196
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,360
or half the empire.

197
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:56,760
That document you presented to the Emperor...

198
00:15:56,760 --> 00:15:57,420
It was fake.

199
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:03,340
Although Prince Ling has been executed,

200
00:16:04,160 --> 00:16:07,020
