201
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:08,640
Our reputation and honor

202
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:12,000
are still tied to the imperial palace.

203
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:16,490
The official records in your hands

204
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,900
are enough to shake the entire court.

205
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:21,620
The Emperor won't just sit and wait for his doom.

206
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,440
Qingshu,

207
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:24,600
