211
00:16:32,880 --> 00:16:33,940
Since the day we two

212
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:35,770
entered the capital together,

213
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:38,160
we have been in the same boat.

214
00:16:38,280 --> 00:16:39,080
Qingshu.

215
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:48,300
